.subckt doublepin A[3] A[2] A[1] A[0] B CK RST Z
*.PININFO A[3:0]:I B:I Z:O RST:I CK:I
x2[3] A[3] Z CK RST NC4 latch
x2[2] A[2] NC1 CK RST NC5 latch
x2[1] A[1] NC2 CK RST NC6 latch
x2[0] A[0] NC3 CK RST NC7 latch
* noconn B
.ends

